                                    <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.1">
                                        <locus from="3r"/>
                                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3588Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of a picture of Mary speaking to a
          worker</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/>ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ገባራዊ፡ ዘኮነ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዕለት፡ ያወትር፡ ሰላማ፡ ለእግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ 
                                            ድንግል፡ በ፪ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ሰርከ፡ ወነግሐ፡ ወመንፈቀ፡ መዓልት፡ ወነበረ፡ ከመዝ፡ ብዙኅ፡ መዋዕል።</incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.2">
                                        <locus from="4ra"/>
                                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3650Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the monk Yoḥannǝs (?) of St
          Macarius who had visions of the Virgin</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/>ወሀሎ፡ ፩ብእሲ፡ ቀሲስ፡ በደብረ፡ መቃርስ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወዘልፍ፡ ታስተርዕዮ፡ 
                                            እግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡ በ፪ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ወትትናገር፡ ወትረ፡ ምስሌሁ፡</incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.3">
                                        <locus from="4va"/>
                                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3599Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the construction of a church in
          Jericho</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/>ወኮነ፡ በሀገረ፡ ጽርዕ፡ ወሀሎ፡ ደብር፡ በጽንፈ፡ ኢያሪኮ፡ ወኑኁ፡ መጠነ፡ መንፈቀ፡ 
                                            ምዕራፍ፡ ወሐለወት፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ በስመ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ቅድስት፡ ድንግል፡</incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.4">
                                        <locus from="6ra"/>
                                        <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3601Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of a rich man from Qʷalāsis who
          fought the Qʷǝz and whose eye was pierced by an arrow</title>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/>ዘኮነ፡ በደሰያት፡ ቆሲይስ፡ ወሀሎ፡ 
                                            ፩ብእ<t:corr xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ሲ</t:corr>፡ ባዕል፡ ጥቀ፡ ወሖረ፡ ሀገረ፡ ትርኵ፡ በሐመር፡ </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                                    <msItem xml:id="p2_i1.5">
                                        <locus from="7rb"/>
                                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3593Miracle">Miracle of Mary: Miracle of the young girl called Mary, from
          Dafrā</title>
                                        <t:note xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">The end is missing.</t:note>
                                        <incipit xml:lang="gez"><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/>ስምዑ፡ አበውየ፡ ወአኀውየ፡ ዘንተ፡ ነገረ፡ ዘኮነ፡ በእንተ፡ እግዝእትነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወላዲተ፡
                                            አምላክ፡ በአማን፡ መሐሪት፡ ወመስተሣህልት፡ ወናዛዚት፡ ለዘሰአለ፡ ኀቤሃ፡ በጥቡእ፡ ልብ፡ ወበጽኑእ፡ ሃይማኖት። ወኮነ፡ እንዘ፡ ሀሎኩ፡ አነ፡ ነዳይ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ 
                                            እስቁፍ፡ በገዳም፡ አስቄጥስ፡ </incipit>
                                    </msItem>
                            </msItem>
